OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWorking from home: Staff   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fabuse it, says City boss   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Andrew Monk, a City chief executive, is
OL,6, not a fan of government proposals for  
OL,7, new staff to have the right to ask to  
OL,8, work from home.                        
OL,10,F"People abuse it," and are less        
OL,11,Fproductive, at least in financial      
OL,12,Fservices, he told the BBC.             
OL,14,FHis view is that a lot of people who   
OL,15,Fask for flexible working want to work  
OL,16,Fpart-time but on a full-time salary.   
OL,18,FThe government, however, says that     
OL,19,Fallowing flexible working makes        
OL,20,Fbusinesses more productive.            
